  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of MCT-SR in Patients With Gastritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Non-inferiority, Phase 3 Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of MCT-SR in Patients With Gastritis</official_title>
